### ================================================================
### STEP 7. 어드민 예약 관리
### OTA 예약 생성 후 실행
### ================================================================

### 전체 예약 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 예약 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ================================================================
### 체크인 (조건: 오늘 날짜 == 체크인 날짜, CONFIRMED 상태)
### ================================================================

POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/1/checkin
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ================================================================
### 체크아웃 (조건: CHECKED_IN 상태, 체크아웃 날짜 이전)
### ================================================================

POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/1/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ================================================================
### 예약 취소 (조건: PENDING 상태만 가능)
### ================================================================

DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/1
Content-Type: application/json
